{"tid":1971071,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有個死肥婆唔識養狗, 比隻狗咬人+咬死左自己第二隻狗","createTime":"2020-04-13T15:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T00:00:06.000Z","uid":30788,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab0804768bd29cf7bd1fbaec1cf88169fd285e9","tid":1971071,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1770355293178992/permalink/2572476402966873/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1770355293178992%2Fpermalink%2F2572476402966873%2F&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B8%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=07e41fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1770355293178992/permalink/2572476402966873/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家小心啲依隻黑色史立莎，先係無端端咬咗我朋友隻狗兩下， 死都唔肯放口 , 之後狗主完全部控制佢自己隻狗 , 要我用力拍咗幾下 佢先肯放口 . 一句對唔住都冇 .<br />\n<br />\n好唔好彩之後又遇到佢哋 仲要攞電話拍返我哋話要公審我哋 講粗口鬧佢, 如果佢唔係咬到我哋隻狗我都唔會鬧佢<br />\n<br />\n之後仲連自己同伴嘅狗都咬住唔放，同埋個主人超有問題，完全冇管教自己隻狗，自己另外一隻狗比隻史立莎咬到仲慢條斯理慢慢行，隻松鼠狗口角有血冇晒反應真係好擔心<br />\n<br />\n大家如果之後遇到佢哋真係要小心啲，我係今日中午喺西貢獅子會遇到佢哋嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>樓主評:  片中D 女人好嘈</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"9744d454af44b884f5d1011179d3768eceea69ae","tid":1971071,"uid":347671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"好明顯係勒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b3e6125da353469e1b8b6f710ecbeabdda1f08","tid":1971071,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:44:34.000Z","msg":"閪人養狗正仆街"},{"pid":"bd7014ae41245c4a2e23cef66cc394f63945efe3","tid":1971071,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"松鼠狗rip"},{"pid":"e27c90cc3b85ef72bf0adb535544e58138487e36","tid":1971071,"uid":225357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T15:48:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec21b6a9c81968f45cfc56a0843d0d30b94fcd3d","tid":1971071,"uid":41524